        <h3>Service Agreements</h3>
        <p>
          Formal services require a written engagement letter or service agreement that outlines:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Scope of services</li>
          <li>Fees and payment terms</li>
          <li>Timeline and deliverables</li>
          <li>Confidentiality obligations</li>
          <li>Termination provisions</li>
